@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gbuvue(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.19 / v2 + 0.72)) * v0)
    tmp = (wp.exp(tmp) / (wp.cos(v2 + 0.63) + wp.cos(v2 + 0.14)))
    v2 = (((v2 + 0.25 - v2 + 0.47) * (v1 + 0.78 * v1 + 0.80)) - wp.sin((v2 + 0.70 + v2 + 0.00)))
    v0 = 0.24
    tmp = (v1 + (tmp - wp.cos(v1 + 0.97)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v2 + 0.89)) - wp.exp(wp.cos(tmp + 0.37)))
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.sin(v2))
    data[tid] = v0
